data.description: TOP FLOOR PENTHOUSE STYLE LIVING!! See the sunrise from the most gorgeous view in the city. THESE VIEWS ARE BREATHTAKING!! HUGE WINDOWS allow lots of natural light. Enjoy resort-style living with ample amenities including a pool, an outdoor living area with grill, a fully equipped gym, theater, business center, clubroom, indoor mail center, doggy park, concierge, valet, an on-site restaurant. The amenities don't stop! This charming top floor condo is conveniently located within walking distance to restaurants, entertainment venues, and shopping centers, with easy access to public transportation and highways. This property features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms offering a cozy and comfortable living space with a thoughtful layout. Newly installed bamboo flooring and new hot water heater. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, solid countertops, new stove, and a built-in air fryer. The open concept living area allows for lots of natural light with balcony access and views from Kennesaw Mountain to the Appalachians, all the way to Stone Mountain!! Add sophistication to your living experience. FIFTY-FIVE INCH TV STAYS!! SEVENTY-FIVE INCH TV STAYS!! WASHER AND DRYER STAY!! Don't miss out on this opportunity to enjoy city living at its finest.
